full_text:
Hi All, Let&#39;s all send out our prayers for Sarah Estep! Thanks, too for the update on her.  =Judy=


--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com, &quot;Guy&quot; &lt;yzzzguy@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt; I just received this note today from the AAEVP:
&gt; 
&gt; &quot;AA-EVP founder, Sarah Estep, was taken to the Hospital on Christmas
&gt;  day.  The doctors have given her just a few days to live.  Her family
&gt;  hopes to bring her home to care for her until her transition. If you 
&gt; want to be kept up to date on this please email us back at ----------,
&gt;  otherwise we will post general information in a second broadcast.  Our
&gt;  prayers are with Sarah for an easy crossing. We know that there will be
&gt;  many who will be waiting to greet her.  Our prayers are also with her
&gt;  family to help them through this difficult time.
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; Tom and Lisa Butler&quot;
&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt; Guy
&gt;
